<div class="ms-workflow-strip__item"><strong>Order</strong><p>Standing, cart, mobile, CSV, SFTP, and EDI orders.</p></div>
<div class="ms-workflow-strip__item"><strong>Cut off</strong><p>Lead times, deadlines, late orders, and controlled changes.</p></div>
<div class="ms-workflow-strip__item"><strong>Fulfil</strong><p>Production, stock, picking, packing, and route delivery.</p></div>
<div class="ms-workflow-strip__item"><strong>Invoice</strong><p>Delivery-based invoices, statements, payments, and exports.</p></div>
<div class="ms-workflow-strip__item"><strong>Report</strong><p>Customer, sales, margin, delivery, and finance visibility.</p></div>
</div>
</div>
